{"tid":1694115,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動post】點樣維持日常抗爭？","createTime":"2019-11-05T03:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T04:12:42.000Z","uid":187902,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eca32e46cc902b4427ee229fd5d8ef12e18ce606","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"蒙面法已經實施咗一個月<br />\n大家平時番工／出街會唔會有呢個疑問︰<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">點解會咁少人響應口罩日／堅持日日戴口罩？</span><br />\n<br />\n歸根究底<br />\n與其話係驚蒙面法（真係因為驚而唔戴嘅應該係少數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n活動<span style=\"color: green;\">參與度低</span>倒不如話係︰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 少人參與造成嘅惡性循環</span></span><br />\n望落咁少人join<br />\n人少就冇辦法有效做到<span style=\"color: orange;\">「抗爭者唔驚蒙面法」</span>嘅效果<br />\n既然做唔到個效果<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁我堅持嚟做咩？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後會落入惡性循環︰<br />\n見到少人參與&gt;&gt;呀A呀B唔想堅持&gt;&gt;見到少人參與&gt;&gt;呀C呀D唔想堅持&gt;&gt;etc...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 惰性</span></span><br />\n星期六日已經攞嚟抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔太想日日都入抗爭狀態</span><br />\n日日返工／返學都要戴嘅話<br />\n好麻煩唔想戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（承1，得自己戴就好似個傻仔傻女咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n目前比較有成效嘅日常抗爭應該係<span style=\"color: orange;\">定期嘅爆買日</span><br />\n想改善上面<span style=\"color: green;\">參與度低</span>呢個問題<br />\n可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">濃縮日常抗爭</span>同<span style=\"color: teal;\">留白</span><br />\n令A活動成為定期活動（目前已經有但未成為每週規律）<br />\n而唔係香港人比較難堅持嘅日日抗爭<br />\n同時預留日子做突發行動／緩衝日<br />\n（姐係呢日喺日程表上一般都係空白）<br />\n畀大家策劃下星期行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如︰<br />\n星期日 大型活動<br />\n星期一　<span style=\"color: teal;\">留白　緩衝</span><br />\n（作用︰留畀突發行動／做文宣／星期日抗爭後嘅休息日）<br />\n星期二　<span style=\"color: orange;\">全民口罩日</span><br />\n（作用︰集體表態「<span style=\"color: orange;\">「唔驚蒙面法」</span>」）<br />\n星期三　<span style=\"color: orange;\">全民文宣日</span><br />\n（作用︰宣傳星期六日大型活動）<br />\n星期四　<span style=\"color: orange;\">爆買感謝日</span><br />\n（作用︰為長遠建立黃色經濟做準備）<br />\n星期五　<span style=\"color: teal;\">留白　緩衝</span><br />\n（作用︰留畀突發行動／為星期六日抗爭養精蓄銳）<br />\n星期六　大型活動<br />\n<br />\n要令日常抗爭真正融入香港人嘅生活<br />\n濃縮同埋有適當嘅留白會係其中一個選擇<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1f1e0837e7e7c218b54906e01c70294253a9dc","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"如果全民大三罷前每星期都做到日常抗爭"},{"pid":"1e3b92d7cea4d68f8f8db7c8e78ffd6a82371595","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"可以話係為大三罷造勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4279a51c933cb6c43fc3d1fd9ad1a11c003354c6","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"畀多啲動力同路人一齊參與大罷工"},{"pid":"7d66c2bf3eda7fe4f8a4163c948b1e5fc45939aa","tid":1694115,"uid":330207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"定期咁集中做某樣野真係會比較有用"},{"pid":"3b4180fee7bed74257590bb8bce18397e388f6ce","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"等於同大家講︰唔會畀你好似個一廂情願嘅傻仔咁自己一個人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0787501499426109239ae09256fa9ab38bbc88","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa7e1255bf0b288b061f1d0716ee4279c124cb14","tid":1694115,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"抗爭成為日常先可以保持到抗爭溫度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbde4bfd3a3c